            <cato:entity-ref entity-type="act" value="National Dam Safety Program Act/s:3/ss:b/p:1">Section 3(b)(1) of such Act</cato:entity-ref> (<external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/33/467a">
              <cato:entity-ref entity-type="uscode" value="usc/33/467a/b/1">33 U.S.C. 467a(b)(1)</cato:entity-ref>
            </external-xref>)</cato:entity> is
			 amended by striking <quote>or maintenance</quote> and inserting
			 <quote>maintenance, condition, or provision for emergency
			 operations</quote>.</text>
			</subsection>
      <subsection id="HC108303D555841DDAA2C75F8EAC313B3">
        <enum>(c)</enum>
        <header>National dam
			 safety program</header>
				<paragraph id="H632837889FA2420091E7F52254E3A8C6">
          <enum>(1)</enum>
          <header>Objectives</header>
          <text>
            <cato:entity xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="law-citation">
              <cato:entity-ref entity-type="act" value="National Dam Safety Program Act/s:8/ss:c/p:4">Section
			 8(c)(4) of such Act</cato:entity-ref> (<external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/33/467f">
                <cato:entity-ref entity-type="uscode" value="usc/33/467f/c/4">33 U.S.C. 467f(c)(4)</cato:entity-ref>
              </external-xref>)</cato:entity> is amended to read as
			 follows:</text>
					<quoted-block id="H94D87C7B95DB402F8492EEFDD9263D7A" style="OLC">
						<paragraph id="H107910642E2048FF9CEC5E77DF55B2FD">
              <enum>(4)</enum>
              <text>develop and
				implement a comprehensive dam safety hazard education and public awareness
				program to assist the public in mitigating against, preparing for, responding
				to, and recovering from dam
				incidents;</text>
						</paragraph>
            <after-quoted-block>.</after-quoted-block>
          </quoted-block>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="HBA93A4ECB86147BD98B7DF065C88B43C">
