                <cato:entity-ref entity-type="uscode" value="usc/33/467f/f/4">33 U.S.C. 467f(f)(4)</cato:entity-ref>
              </external-xref>)</cato:entity> is amended by inserting <quote>,
			 representatives from nongovernmental organizations,</quote> after <quote>State
			 agencies</quote>.</text>
				</paragraph>
      </subsection>
